================================================================
================== profiling tools:=============================
================================================================
gprof notes

create performance based ELF file:
  generate object file:
     g++  hello_world.cpp -c -g -pg==> will get hello_world.o
  generate ELF file:
    g++ hello_world.o -g -pg -o hello
  execute it:
    ./hello
  get performance statistics:
    gprof hello

